<section id="difference" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-light-gray">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-deep-navy">We're Not a Faceless Franchise. We're Your Neighbours.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-light-sky rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-handshake text-fresh-sky text-xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-deep-navy mb-2">Our 100% Bond Back Guarantee</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-warm-700">If your property manager flags any cleaning-related issue within 72 hours, we return to fix it—free of charge. That's our promise.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-light-sky rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-home text-fresh-sky text-xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-deep-navy mb-2">Local & Family Run</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-warm-700">"We're not a big franchise; we're your neighbours. I'm Trent and my quality-control expert is Pandora the Lab! When you call us, you get a dedicated local team."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-light-sky rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-award text-fresh-sky text-xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-deep-navy mb-2">5+ Years of Know-How</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-warm-700">We know the real estate checklists inside and out. We clean for the fussiest agents, ensuring no spots are missed.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-light-sky rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-fresh-sky text-xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-deep-navy mb-2">Complete Peace of Mind</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-warm-700">Your property is always protected. We are fully insured for public liability, giving you one less thing to worry about.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-light-sky rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-leaf text-fresh-sky text-xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-deep-navy mb-2">Pet & Family Safe Cleaning</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-warm-700">Our solutions deliver a professional-grade clean while being formulated to be biodegradable and safe for all surfaces.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border-2 border-fresh-sky text-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-light-sky rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto">
