                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-deep-navy mb-2">The Pandora Paw of Approval</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-warm-700">Every clean is personally checked to meet our high standards—and to get the final nod from our furry supervisor.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>